                        Easily tracking injuries by job sites, clients, and/or company branch offices. Say goodbye to the endless mounds of paperwork, injury files and bills. Everything is at your finger tips from one digital employee file. Managers can update injuries from anywhere when the rumors start flying about a fraudulent injury. CompCore turns every manger into a safety manger, making your life easier.
                    </p>
