            <div class="row feature ss">
                <div class="span6 info">
                    <h3>
                        <img src="/assets/features-ico6.png" />
                        Bill Tracking and Payment
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Medical providers, Attorneys, and another service provider can submit bills directly into the injured employees file within CompCore. This lets you track every penny per claim so you can see with one click every cost. Your TPA or Insurance claims adjuster can access the employee file to pull bills for bill rearview and/or make notes about a claim. By staying in the loop on where your money is going, keeps people honest and more money in your pocket.  
                    </p>
                </div>
