                        <img src="/assets/features-ico3.png" />
                        Easy Reporting & Claim tracking
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        From the main dashboard see how many claims are open and how old. View recent updates by team members and claim adjusters. Easily run year end OSAH 300 logs with one click, or see if certain clients or job sites are having too many injury and your losing money. Track employee follow up appointments and coordinate with doctors to get employees released to full duty faster.</p>
                </div>
             </div>

  <div class="row feature ss">
                <div class="span6 info">
                    <h3>
                        <img src="/assets/features-ico2.png" />
                        Collaborate with everyone!
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Finally a tool that lets safety managers, branch managers, supervisors, medical providers and insurance claim adjusters stay in constant contact to better manage claims and lower costs. Medical providers can submit status reports electronically to the injury profile and your team can add/review notes at any time. Letting everyone on your team stay up to date with the most current information without ever having a piece of paper cross your desk.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="span6">
                    <img src="/assets/showcase2.png" class="pull-right" />
                </div>
            </div>
  
